Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:11.45,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next up is batter number 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:15.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a listless, boring day during the peak of summer right after Obon had just passed. {TL Note: Obon is a major festival, usually occurring in August, in Japan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:22.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On TV, there was a match between two teams and, although I had never heard of either of them before,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:27.78,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I began to feel sympathy for the losing team and I started rooting for them for some odd reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then, my mobile began to ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:36.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're free today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're all meeting in front of the station at exactly 2 o' clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She cut me off completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:47.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How did she know I was free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Despite how I look, I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:53.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I don't really have anything to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.86,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hit! It's going, going! Over left field!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.17,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And it's out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:00:59.84,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:01.22,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:04.15,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bring your swimsuit and come on your bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:06.11,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And bring plenty of money, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:07.74,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all. Over~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:09.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:12.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.17,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kashima just finished rounding third base...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.94,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pitcher Suzuki seems to be crumpled in a state of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:21.33,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is quite a painful sight to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:22.86,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tragic, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:25.37,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And it's their final year too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.42,0:01:26.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:28.13,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His teammates seemed to have lost their voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:31.14,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The pitcher doesn't offer even a single word of consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:33.30,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With that, the score is 8 - 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.48,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This has become quite a torturous battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.35,Haruhi Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(480,400)\pos(285,379)}Endless Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.90,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're late, Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.19,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't you put more effort into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.70,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.51,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You made the Brigade Chief wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.29,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Penalty, I say! Penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.65,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I even made sure to come 15 minutes early...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.63,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why am I always last?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.90,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, now that everyone's here, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.34,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koizumi-kun, you'll carry Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuki and I will sit behind Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.43,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just asking, but where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.14,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The public pool, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.68,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since it's summer, we should have summer activities like what people do in the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.57,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can't get back the time we waste,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.57,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so we're going to go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:02.08,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is our once-in-a-lifetime freshman summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wasted time, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:19.00,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, the smell of chlorine. It feels just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.83,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.05,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.42,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No Diving - Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.25,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry up and get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.56,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The water's warm, and feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:38.06,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can't she see the signs that say "No Diving" all over the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.61,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But this is a good thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:46.13,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't you think Suzumiya-san may have found a normal way of enjoying things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:51.29,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She called me to go out all of a sudden, and then hung up on me after stating her one-sided demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.37,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't exactly say that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:57.96,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, seeing as Suzumiya-san is laughing so joyfully like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.50,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there shouldn't be anything happening that will endanger the world. {Not sure about these two lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.75,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only that were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.83,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.51,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing problematic has happened since that trip we took.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:17.05,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At the moment, for Suzumiya-san and the rest of us, the world is at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.70,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's have lunch soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.66,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've got Mikuru-chan's homemade sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.58,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's very tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.25,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.62,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to take another piece of fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.83,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan, pass me the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.06,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Indeed, it is peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.42,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.08,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:49.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'd be more appropriate to call this place a "pool for the masses" than a "pool for the public". {TL Note: In Japanese, public (shimin) sounds a bit like masses (shomin)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:49.05,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Note: In Japanese, public (shimin) sounds a bit like masses (shomin)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.46,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on! What are you doing, Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spending summer vacation like this isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.53,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.62,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These are my brigade members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.61,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They'll listen to everything, so tell them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.81,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.99,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I came up with an action plan for us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:18.75,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.46,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:24.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An itinerary for how we should spend what little remains of summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.49,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For the SOS Brigade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.42,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.29,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's only two more weeks left of summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.56,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}even though there's still a bunch of stuff that I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.30,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're getting serious from here on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.01,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hmm, I see. "Activities we must do during summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:45.86,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Summer club retreat, pool, Obon festival, fireworks festival, part-time job, stargazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.81,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a lot of stuff, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:52.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And we've got to do everything listed here in two weeks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there anything else that you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.22,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... I want to scoop up goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.67,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay! "Goldfish scooping."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.59,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll start carrying this out tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.08,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, does anyone know if there's going to be an Obon festival happening nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.28,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd like to have a fireworks festival too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At least research these things before we carry them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.71,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:15.17,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll contact you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.83,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and don't forget about goldfish scooping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.06,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a passionate desire of Mikuru-chan's, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:20.90,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do I always end up paying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.76,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were late, so isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't make us wait again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.62,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, you're all dismissed for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.20,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Man... does that mean we're going to be messing around every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:50.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next morning, the call that woke me up from my indolence was, once again, from Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.68,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've figured out where they're going to have an Obon festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.68,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The time: tonight. Location: the Civic Stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:07.10,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just when I was thinking about how unbelievable the timing was, Haruhi suddenly said:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's all go buy yukatas together! {TL Note: Yukata is a type of summer kimono.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:15.07,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan and Yuki don't have one, and I saw some cheap ones in a shop, so let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:21.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi selfishly picked out yukatas for Asahina-san and Nagato, and rushed off to the changing rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is taking quite a bit of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:32.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The three of them finally finished changing after we endured an hour of the other female customers avoiding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.67,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:39.76,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They match you girls very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.52,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course! I picked them out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.67,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Especially Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.79,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just what I'd expect from myself! It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.51,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My eyes can never be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:56.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Among the various costumes Haruhi has forced on her, this certainly is top class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And it really suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:03.26,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So this is the traditional dress of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.21,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a bit tight on the chest, but it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.50,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With this, our preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.67,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To the Obon festival venue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, man, the Obon festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's been ages since I last saw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:26.37,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah! Mikuru-chan! They've got the goldfish scooping that you wanted to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.95,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just keep scooping non-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.91,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You get 200 points if you get the one with black eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:35.15,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shall we do the same? How about a competition to see who can catch more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.56,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.28,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm more interested in the food stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.42,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What about you, Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.67,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want to get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.15,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're interested in that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:54.94,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.40,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? Sure! 800 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.72,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thirteen of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:07.21,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a large haul, but we didn't need all of them, so we just took one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.00,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't catch a single one, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.99,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Goldfish scooping is pretty hard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:15.82,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no. Normally, you wouldn't get that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.50,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's easy if you get the hang of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.53,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? What's up with that mask, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.08,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see. But why that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They were probably on the same wavelength or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.14,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:36.24,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We haven't gone that way, so let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.45,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You still want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.84,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.62,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.99,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll only let you have one, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.56,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tasty? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:20.24,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, we've pretty much seen all of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.89,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's do fireworks next! Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:28.56,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since we went through all the trouble of dressing up, we might as well make the most of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.91,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.94,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was a shop over there selling them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.18,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.09,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.36,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.87,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.87,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Note: Kakizaki Hayao from the "SDF Macross: Do You Remember Love?" movie was blown up by missiles while making fun of women
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:07.02,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.11,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Obon festival. Fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.37,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.26,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, we're going to go catch bugs tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:18.22,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi, fun and games are fine and all, but did you finish your summer homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Says me, who hasn't even touched his yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:22.06,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:25.40,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I finished all of that in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:25.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I finished it in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:33.66,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Finish all that tedious stuff so you can actually enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.87,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the right way to enjoy summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is this person so smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The distribution of attributes is pretty random.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.36,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, we're catching bugs tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The person who catches the most gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.43,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:52.09,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The position of Brigade Chief for one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ew, no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.02,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So it counts as long as it's any kind of bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:59.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hm... cicada's only!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:03.52,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, this'll be the SOS Brigade's cicada catching competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.98,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The person with the most wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To make sure it would rain, I put up a teru teru bozu, but unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.37,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Note: Teru teru bozu is a small ghost-like doll made from cloth made as a charm for good weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it was a ridiculously nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.84,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No doubt, the cicadas must be enjoying the day with what could be considered the best temperature of this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.19,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come to think of it, cicadas are edible, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.23,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Would they taste good as tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try that by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:37.82,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, I've thought about this occasionally, but isn't tempura only good because of the batter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.43,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does that mean cicadas would taste good too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apologize! Apologize to all the tempura chefs in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:52.37,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First of all, isn't it weird to see five high school students gathered around with bug nets and cages?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.33,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:57.65,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can't catch cicadas without bug nets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.47,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's start then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.58,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The winner gets to be Brigade Chief for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.02,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.13,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like she really wants to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.68,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:17.43,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Geez. I haven't gone bug catching since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.28,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.80,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.74,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, you've caught one already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.77,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not a cicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.50,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.45,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A Hercules?  {TL Note: A Hercules beetle is a very famous and rare type of rhinoceros beetle.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.45,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Note: A Hercules beetle is a very famous and rare type of rhinoceros beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.79,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Announcing the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan: one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuki: four.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.33,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koizumi-kun: seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kyon: nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.05,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And the person with the highest score is:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to say it. We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.41,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me with twelve!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:32.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like the position of Brigade Chief won't go to anyone else for even a day! Sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:36.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me you seriously want to make tempura out of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? You want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.55,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.62,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.77,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We should probably go with a "catch-and-release" mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:48.45,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They might repay us with a favor in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:53.18,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here. Go back to the mountains! Don't get caught again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:04.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, wait. That was a moving scene and all, but all you did was catch and then release them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:14.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruhi found us some work somewhere, and made sure we all had a part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was the annual sale at a local supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:18.89,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were supposed to attract customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:27.97,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:28.60,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:39.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why? Why is it that even I have to dress up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't there a more suitable job to do during summer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Haruhi's leisurely profiting from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we have to deal with this sort of arrangement again, there's going to be a rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.65,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now I understand how snakes feel when they shed their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.81,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.98,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The manager was also happy with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.38,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need his gratitude. What about the pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.96,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.40,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This costume was the pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.03,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been wanting this for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.54,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He said he'd give it to me because of Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:21.56,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I'll decorate the club room with this frog in commemoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.41,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan, you can wear this whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.29,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I give you my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Obon festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:33.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bug catching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:34.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next activity Haruhi decided on was stargazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:43.06,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So this is a telescope from this time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.82,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't seem so different from the ones used in Kepler's period.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I think it's probably very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you just buy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:54.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No. This was a hobby of mine when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:58.58,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I first saw Jupiter's moons, I was quite touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.44,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I found it. Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.74,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.71,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Martians!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.62,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't really want them to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:16.00,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just imagine stupid octopus monsters wiggling around as they plot the conquer of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.76,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't imagine being an alien being fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.35,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.49,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They could be a really friendly bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:27.39,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They must be living quietly in a giant cave underground. It's a testament to their timidness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.93,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're probably doing it so they don't scare us humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:34.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Exactly how modest are these Martians that you've got in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.14,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Enough about Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.35,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's look for UFOs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:43.58,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since they're after Earth, there must be scouts keeping watch somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.31,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on! Help me out, Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:50.04,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Wha? UFO, UFO...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:00.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And summer vacation continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The next thing Haruhi said was:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.72,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go to the batting center!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:08.77,Haruhi Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Note: Koushien is the name of the famous high school baseball championships in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:08.77,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I saw the Koushien on the news this morning, it hit me. {TL Note: Koushien is the name of the famous high school baseball championships in Japan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.76,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We shouldn't be satisfied with sandlot baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:17.01,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We, the SOS Brigade, should aim for the National League!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What an impressive person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where does she get all her energy from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:36.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps the mitochondria in her cells are different from that of a normal person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only she'd spend that energy on something beneficial to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.41,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:55.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Afterwards, since no one was able to hit the pause button while Haruhi aimed to achieve her quota, we continued day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We even went to a real fireworks show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:06.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There, we enjoyed the sight of flaming flowers flying up and going "boom" around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:13.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}On a different day, we participated in a goby fishing contest by the river district border.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.79,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mikuru-chan! The pole! The pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.32,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave it to me. I'll retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:33.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's more. We held a test of courage, which, as a matter of fact, is a standard routine but no one actually does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:42.47,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We went to see an overrated summer blockbuster that was advertised everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:50.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We also went to the beach at the peak of jellyfish season.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:56.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We had a punishment game of bowling entitled: "No One Can Leave Until Everyone Had Gotten a Strike."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:03.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And a long, endurance karaoke marathon that tested the limits of our throats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I get the feeling I mixed in some completely irrelevant events,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:17.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but, anyway, we still spent two weeks of summer vacation having as much fun as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:25.42,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Today, we've reached August 30th,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.20,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and we've pretty much gone through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good grief. It ended safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.75,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is just this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:37.35,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But... well, I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.65,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say, is there anything in particular you guys want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:40.99,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing in particular for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.58,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.51,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to take some time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.16,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.26,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.40,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:53.27,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did a lot this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:57.06,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We went to lots of places, wore yukatas, and even caught a bunch of cicadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.46,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:04.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does she still have some lingering regret or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.88,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:11.39,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're on-call tomorrow, but you can stay home and rest if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:15.78,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll meet in the club room the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:33.64,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap. I haven't done any of my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:45.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}August 31st. The last day of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:49.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seeing as it was impossible for me to finish all of my homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:52.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and that I was tired from playing around so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I spent the day indulging myself by lounging around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:03.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:09.88,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, I don't care. Whatever happens, happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:29.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Guess I'll sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:31.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}School starts tomorrow, after all.
